{"tid":1542040,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"[有片] 手足落單, 俾休班狗狂打頭","createTime":"2019-09-04T17:31:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-04T17:55:10.000Z","uid":11454,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"444784186996de86aa755d9c790f57f965e6bb54","tid":1542040,"uid":11454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T17:31:24.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/davidchan123/videos/2410496559041362/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fdavidchan123%2Fvideos%2F2410496559041362%2F&d=Fy0o8YzXie14Yexn7W6ruQDrJ99PsHpDQ3gYSBhgLgU%3D&h=44ed9ebf\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/davidchan123/videos/2410496559041362/</a><br />\n<ins>前因</ins><br />\n手足寶琳爆閘, 撞正港鐵站長<br />\n圍左站長5-10分鐘<br />\n突然開始混亂, 有人出手<br />\n手足試圖制服站長, 絕對冇打,只係夾住佢<br />\n有手足話就快有狗到<br />\n但有幾個冇即時走<br />\n之後10秒後就有狗沖落月台<br />\n<br />\n點解要唔戀戰<br />\n點解要快速私了<br />\n點解要救人<br />\n<br />\n狗係會睇LIVE, 你睇到佢都睇到<br />\n個個站控制室都有狗, 由其係大站, 高危站<br />\n由圍站長到有狗到, 前後15-20分鐘<br />\n咁就拉左2個手足<br />\n唔講送頭, 但絕對係不必要既損失<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2b2d609d71638e4d4f1ff8d4edeedf652c4eb8e","tid":1542040,"uid":167277,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T17:34:45.000Z","msg":"不要被仇恨支配 ..."},{"pid":"1ec753a172417e3f8b95763a695481630999c967","tid":1542040,"uid":11454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T17:34:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf50ac6f1a0bff5933edec90dec99b6c3f9bed20","tid":1542040,"uid":104507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T17:35:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />要愛惜自己呀手足"},{"pid":"266caae2f505f970954977a04c8aa1d3530a9548","tid":1542040,"uid":108347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T17:37:04.000Z","msg":"果個似係藍絲?定係個站長黎?"},{"pid":"446a08416d53a1aa28da636670d3026bf0db825e","tid":1542040,"uid":11454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"266caae2f505f970954977a04c8aa1d3530a9548","tid":1542040,"uid":108347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T17:37:04.000Z","msg":"果個似係藍絲?定係個站長黎?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T17:38:22.000Z","msg":"藍格仔衫似係休班警<br />\n站長俾黑警護送走左"},{"pid":"851a8e687733766f72b905785358768f6a70da72","tid":1542040,"uid":38957,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T17:39:21.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"cc01c5ba92c34ecf7ff94f079d67103db7482cdd","tid":1542040,"uid":11454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b2b2d609d71638e4d4f1ff8d4edeedf652c4eb8e","tid":1542040,"uid":167277,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T17:34:45.000Z","msg":"不要被仇恨支配 ..."},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T17:44:20.000Z","msg":"俾藍絲打, 想還手, 人之常情<br />\n但要控制自己既情緒, 要用理性作出適合既判斷<br />\n情緒主導思考係好危險, 唔好令自己身陷險境"},{"pid":"18f0862de1d4c54b31470b938a50438d106c9b23","tid":1542040,"uid":11454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T17:50:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ad8478a3146f6febd9e14352b47a912192bc678","tid":1542040,"uid":306354,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T17:55:10.000Z","msg":"其實站入面係有警員室<br />\n間中會有兩三狗當值<br />\n但而家應該每晚都有幾隻入左去<br />\n之前香港之路果晚<br />\n元朗站曾經見過有6、7隻狗係站內<br />\n當時黨鐵比左佢地入會議室到候命<br />\n所以係高危既站入面係有機會有好多狗<br />\n等緊手足入閘<br />\n一入閘佢地就可以大堂封站再包圍<br />\n同時佢地都可以用黨鐵月台出口突襲<br />\n即使上面有手足睇水<br />\n但狗直接月台出同大堂出<br />\n手足都冇可能走得切<br />\n所以盡可能唔好入閘<br />\n即使入閘都唔好入得太深<br />\n要預隨時跳閘走人<br />\n快閃&amp;唔入閘係最好方法"}]}